des: The Newtown Rail Trail is a project to convert 8.5 miles in Bucks County along the right of way for SEPTA’s former Newtown/Fox Chase Rail Line, which has been unused since 1983. Updated frequently with news, this Alexa Skill is your go to source for information about the project.
